message:
This is why we do the work we do. Human Trafficking isn't only growing in Tennessee, it's happening all across the country.
“Human trafficking touches just about every county in Tennessee and the average age of victims when they begin is 13-years-old”
#lawenforcement #humantrafficking #Education
